working hard to keep Los Feliz Hills School open despite monthly deficits of 
$14,000 to $20,000. TORU KAWANA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Barbara Rasmussen, 
left, scrapes paint from wall at Los Feliz Hills School. 
</P>
