MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; AFGHANISTAN -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; 
AFGHANISTAN -- MILITARY AID -- USSR; AFGHANISTAN -- RELIEF; REFUGEES -- 
AFGHANISTAN; CASUALTIES; STATISTICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
