SCHOOLS -- STATE AID; EDUCATION -- STATE AID; PROPOSITION 98 (SCHOOL DISTRICT 
FUNDS); CALIFORNIA -- CONSTITUTIONS; CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS; CALIFORNIA -- 
BUDGET; CALIFORNIA -- FINANCES 
</P>
