<DOCID> 19374 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 16, 1989, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part 4; Page 3; Column 2; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
643 words 
</P>
