<P>
Savanna 91, Azusa 70 -- Sophomore forward Mustapha Abdi scored 35 points and 
had 13 rebounds to lead the Rebels at Savanna. The Rebels (24-2), champions of 
the Orange League, will face Trabuco Hills on Friday in the second round. 
